This Week's Podcast- TB284 
The #COVID19 pandemic ends with widespread vaccine compliance, but a formidable misinformation campaign seeks to derail public health efforts. I speak with Dr. Rahul Gupta from March of Dimes about #vaccine hesitancy. @DrGuptaMD https://t.co/Ne9qHRkMy5 https://t.co/YLRBzfFkym
